# User Stories

| Story ID | User Story                                                                    | Acceptance Criteria                     | Priority |
| -------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------- | -------- |
| US-001   | As a student, I want to register an account so that I can use the system      | Account is created successfully         | High     |
| US-002   | As a student, I want to log in so that I can access my assignments            | Login successful with valid credentials | High     |
| US-003   | As a student, I want to add assignments so that I can track my work           | Assignment is saved correctly           | High     |
| US-004   | As a student, I want to edit assignments so that I can update details         | Changes are saved                       | Medium   |
| US-005   | As a student, I want to delete assignments so that I can remove tasks         | Assignment is deleted                   | Medium   |
| US-006   | As a student, I want to view all assignments so that I can manage my tasks    | Assignments displayed clearly           | High     |
| US-007   | As a student, I want reminders so that I do not miss deadlines                | Notification sent before deadline       | High     |
| US-008   | As a student, I want to mark assignments complete so that I track progress    | Status updated                          | Medium   |
| US-009   | As a student, I want to search assignments so that I can find them quickly    | Results display within 2 seconds        | Medium   |
| US-010   | As an admin, I want user data secured so that the system is safe              | Data encrypted                          | High     |
| US-011   | As a system, I want fast response times so that users have a smooth experience| Response ≤ 2 seconds                    | Medium   |
